{"tid":1361573,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"見議地鐵不合作運動","createTime":"2019-07-24T15:40:23.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-24T23:55:57.000Z","uid":94369,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"d934c2e82ae4368e1d27798c726c5f212cd42374","tid":1361573,"uid":94369,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-24T15:40:23.000Z","msg":"煩忙時間站內外叫口號<br />\n光復香港 時代革命<br />\n1.香港人搵食行先，阻人返工唔係咁好<br />\n2.港人善忙，叫口號可以提醒大家件事未完<br />\n3.其他途人應該都會抽下水一齊叫口號，就好似今晚場波咁，等佢地覺得自己都係革命嘅一份子，比佢地出下post，文宣下都唔錯<br />\n4.即管比CCTVB報新聞啦，不停loop口號，睇下佢點cut段片<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />支持<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />反對"},{"pid":"b13ba0450b0cc0eabbc3aef6764363aab7324978","tid":1361573,"uid":42250,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-24T15:43:40.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=Y9NSf3UDygg\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3DY9NSf3UDygg&d=oilSAI4QurnOyWEhgxZI0Dk5r7V16zLonem%2BWgH46Yg%3D&h=a63db166\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=Y9NSf3UDygg</a>"},{"pid":"ce1fab96103c0cbadfb38112f8f548447e4315fa","tid":1361573,"uid":216789,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-24T15:52:45.000Z","msg":"<strong>慎防黑惡勢力蔓延禍港，提防本地非法操縱妓女賣淫集團</strong><br />\n<br />\n鑒於近日有無辜香港市民慘遭黑勢力人仕襲擊，現懇切呼籲各香港市民不論男女，請慎防本地非法操縱妓女賣淫集團，保障自身安全，萬事小心，<strong><span style=\"color: red;\">切忌助長黑惡勢力氣焰</span></strong>"},{"pid":"413440a6439d22f2b916528c522475f14d8414fb","tid":1361573,"uid":53003,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-24T16:27:41.000Z","msg":"在入閘前聚集一班人，全部跳入閘，有冇得諗？"},{"pid":"3f992dbdbbe80723565a4d6325357fe1e5a0812b","tid":1361573,"uid":177695,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-24T23:55:57.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/hUTcv7D.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FhU